songs.title: No Romance
songs.lyrics:

Lean, lean, drop
Gucci flops
She know I get cash
I don’t trust a lot
Gengar cup (purp)
Big bands in my vault
Leanin, walk
In these Saint Laurents
She a dancer
No romancer
High as NASA
I can’t land (ah)
This the xan love
This the xan love
You don’t trust me
I don’t trust me either too

Told her that I love her, then I leave her
I turned every doubter to a believer
I stand 6'2" in McQueens (yuh)
Diamonds on me, aquafina
Neck piece like a freezer
5 stacks for the Jesus

Pour the lean by the liter

Lean, lean, drop
Gucci flops
She know I get cash
I don’t trust a lot

Big bands in my vault
Leanin, walk
In these Saint Laurents
She a dancer
No romancer
High as NASA
I can’t land (ah)
This the xan love
This the xan love

[Outro]
Dancing with the demons and the divas
